}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "UF-214D-IOGLA-051111" is silkscreened on the board. This is presumed to be an '''Action Star''' UF-214D. :The '''[[Genesys Logic]]''' hub IC package is marked with "GL850A", "MS2DC03G06", "728A82819".
The IEEE 1394 hub is controlled by the on-board '''[[Texas Instruments]]''' TSB41AB3.
The power adapter included with the device is a Sunny Switching Adapter SYS1298-1305-W2 (100-240VAC~1.0A MAX, 30VA, 50-60Hz -> 5VDC 2.6A).
